        agentList() {
            const self = this
            const endpointList = []
            this.reprocessList.forEach((externalKey2) => {

        },
        getAgent() {
            this.agentList();
            axios.all(this.$store.getters.endpoint.map((endpoints) => axios.put(endpoints)))
            .then((data) => console.log(data))
        }
    }
